text: Nemani Nagusi (born 21 July 1988) is a Fiji rugby union player. His usual position is as a Flanker, and he currently plays for Newcastle Falcons. ==References== ==External links== *itsrugby.co.uk Profile Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Fijian rugby union players Category:Fiji international rugby union players Category:Rugby union flankers
